data.title: Tull Family
data.text:
Sixth Generation

23. Robert Count Of6 Vermandois {[AND MEAUX]} (Herbert Ii, Count5, Herbert I, Count4, Pepin Ii Quentin,3, Bernard, King Of2 Italy, Pippin (Carloman), King1) was born in of, Vermandois, normandy, France about 911. Robert died August 29, 968 at 57 years of age.

He married Adelais "Were" Countess Vermandois before 956. Adelais was born in of, Bourgogne, Marneogne, France about 914. Adelais was the daughter of Gilbert Gislebert Of Burgundy [Duke of] and Ermengarde Burgundy. Adelais died August 19, 967 at 53 years of age. Adelais was baptized a member of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints November 6, 1991. Temple Code: SLAKE. She was endowed November 12, 1991. Temple Code: SLAKE.

Robert was baptized a member of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints October 17, 1931. Temple Code: temple code unknown. He was endowed March 8, 1933. Temple Code: temple code unknown.

Robert Count Of Vermandois [AND MEAUX] and Adelais "Were" Countess Vermandois had the following children:

29 i. Archambaud De7 Vermandois was born in of, Vermandois, normandy, France about 930. Archambaud died August 29, 968 at 38 years of age. Archambaud was baptized a member of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints July 21, 1941. Temple Code: LG. He was endowed October 17, 1941. Temple Code: LG.

30 ii. Herbert De Vermandois was born in of, Vermandois, normandy, France about 932. Herbert died April 23, 994 at 61 years of age. He married twice. He married an unknown person. He married Mrs-Herbert De Vermandois.

Herbert was baptized a member of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints July 21, 1941. Temple Code: LG. He was endowed October 17, 1941. Temple Code: LG. He was sealed to his parents November 6, 1991. Temple Code: SLAKE.

31 iii. Adelaide De Vermandois [Countess of Anj was born in of, Vermandois, normandy, France about 934. Adelaide died after 982. She married twice. She married Lambert D' Autun in France, about 945. Lambert and Adelaide De Vermandois [Countess of Anj were sealed December 7, 1954. Temple Code: temple code unknown. She married Geoffroy I "Grisegonnelle" Anjou in France, March 2, 979. Geoffroy was born in of, Anjou, France about 938. Geoffroy was the son of Foulques Ii "Le Anjou and Gerberge Du Maine. Geoffroy died July 21, 987 at 49 years of age. Geoffroy was baptized a member of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints November 27, 1937. Temple Code: SL. He was endowed March 31, 1938. Temple Code: SL. (See Geoffroy I "Grisegonnelle" Anjou for the continuation of this line.)

Adelaide was baptized a member of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints April 24, 1935. Temple Code: SG. She was endowed April 25, 1935. Temple Code: SG. Adelaide and Lambert D' Autun were sealed December 7, 1954. Temple Code: temple code unknown.
